    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-09-30T16:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-09-30T16:00:00-05:00" n="361"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d361">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">840.48 Refugees/4522: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Sweden</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Stockholm</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-09-30T22:00:00+01:00"
                            >September 30, 1943—10 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received October 1—8:24 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3149. Foreign Office states it learned yesterday from what is considered
                    authentic sources that Germans plan to send Silohous [<hi rend="italic"
                    >sic</hi>] and Jews from Denmark to Reich. Only newspaper item covering this
                    today was short reference in editorial in <hi rend="italic">Svenska
                        Dagbladet</hi> which said that recent Danish refugees coming to Sweden
                    believe that by this threat Germans are trying to blackmail King and Danish
                    Parliament to establish legal government.</p>
                <p>Foreign Office has instructed its Minister in Berlin today to approach German
                    Government and state that if this transfer were put into effect it would have
                    very unfortunate effect on public opinion in Sweden. Minister is instructed to
                    state Swedish Government is prepared to receive these Jews in Sweden and if
                    German Government fears they might exercise influence of political nature
                    Swedish Government <pb facs="0369" n="359" xml:id="pg_359"/> is prepared to
                    intern them. Foreign Office has asked for immediate reply and hopes to have
                    something today.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
